{"id": 2498, "genre": 1001, "title": "作为一个当代青年你都体会过哪些无形“紧箍咒”？", "description": "你认为如今怎样可以被称为「现代奴隶」?", "record_count": 5380, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180803125516ZnvJ0yBsil1EGQpM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-04T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 302080, "content": "沉默损失严重", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}, {"id": 302336, "content": "完全不明白酒怎么就是交流感情了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461623}, {"id": 302082, "content": "眼见着堂姐刚生头胎就被念叨以后两个孩子怎样怎样", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449167}, {"id": 302338, "content": "以爱之名的安排", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462408}, {"id": 302083, "content": "所有点子想法都已经被实践证实过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348719}, {"id": 302339, "content": "被标准化的成功", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462408}, {"id": 302084, "content": "生活和赚钱是两码事，生活是生活，赚钱是赚钱。两样都需要是用心经营，很显然还需要多付出", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461195}, {"id": 302340, "content": "每天往返在学校和家里两点一线的路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462423}, {"id": 302085, "content": "整个社会都严重的走形式，几千年的官僚主义根本没有变动", "image": null, "praise_count": 295, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440360}, {"id": 302341, "content": "天天除了学习，吃饭，睡觉，玩手机，看看书感觉就没别的事干了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462426}, {"id": 302086, "content": "是都准备好面对生活的不确定性", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461199}, {"id": 302342, "content": "你该做这个 女孩子就得会做这些 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462002}, {"id": 302087, "content": "孝心就是不可以发表自己的意见🙅‍♀️", "image": null, "praise_count": 174, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460710}, {"id": 302343, "content": "房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084704}, {"id": 302088, "content": "在学校里就开始打官腔", "image": null, "praise_count": 223, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426410}, {"id": 302344, "content": "父母总是以生了你为理由告诉你按照他们说的做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462489}, {"id": 302600, "content": "买了房之后 表面上好像大家觉得你有了保障 实际上生活直接过成了屎 什么兴趣爱好 生活标准 通通给房贷让路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195977}, {"id": 302856, "content": "明明自己不想做的事。总有人会强行拉着你做", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465877}, {"id": 302089, "content": "KPI", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251294}, {"id": 302090, "content": "上辈人的期望。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461202}, {"id": 302091, "content": "为了经济自由放弃下班时间的自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459648}, {"id": 302347, "content": "每天都是过着重复的生活感到麻木", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438388}, {"id": 302092, "content": "明明某组织的领导跟屎一样又臭又蠢，咱人民还得抛弃一定的亲情，时间，空间等辛苦的工作，生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186803}, {"id": 302093, "content": "网游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636017}, {"id": 302349, "content": "好奇心和想象力被父母扼杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462546}, {"id": 302094, "content": "想飞得更高，却没有风\n想走的更远，却没有路\n人的一生，运气最重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461217}, {"id": 302350, "content": "女孩子不结婚很丢人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462561}, {"id": 316174, "content": "舔狗其实才能拥有自尊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529978}, {"id": 302095, "content": "大学生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1452914}, {"id": 302351, "content": "明明离职了，怕家里唠叨。又得骗说还有工作，可是手头的银子越来越少……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235651}, {"id": 302096, "content": "我的以后被安排。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408500}, {"id": 302352, "content": "婚姻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462575}, {"id": 302097, "content": "今年17，但我的以后被出生安排。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408500}, {"id": 302353, "content": "初恋过后的第四年，谈了大我七岁的男盆友，彼此喜欢，想结婚。父母反对，只看了照片，说不仅年纪大，还又丑又矮，一看就不是好人。不肯见面，不肯我继续交往。我的婚姻我想要自己做决定，可是不想和父母反面。我们都很难受，不知怎么办。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462574}, {"id": 302098, "content": "像我这种穷比，当然是房子了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461220}, {"id": 302354, "content": "有些选修课和shi一样，你tm还挂了\n其他专业课还行，绩点却差了一截", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438763}, {"id": 302099, "content": "高房价下的生活魔咒", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461173}, {"id": 302355, "content": "贫穷贫穷贫穷\n唉\n贫穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438763}, {"id": 302100, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461228}, {"id": 302356, "content": "女孩子就应该化妆，就应该很会打扮，就应该穿高跟鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349359}, {"id": 302868, "content": "分数 高考", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376950}, {"id": 302101, "content": "抵御各种阴暗面的力量", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429940}, {"id": 302102, "content": "有用强迫症。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460182}, {"id": 302103, "content": "不知道如何选择，如何放弃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339512}, {"id": 302359, "content": "学校里面到处都是形式主义，无处藏身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317277}, {"id": 302104, "content": "我在面对一个打 字 不 用 负 责的年代", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315229}, {"id": 302360, "content": "向现实低头 我能有梦但是我和我的梦走不远", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455655}, {"id": 302105, "content": "贫穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456951}, {"id": 302106, "content": "做的所有事都被人指指点点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449713}, {"id": 302362, "content": "不管对方有多不好，可和我比起来还是比我好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462662}]}